  <brief_title>Effect of the Pneumoperitoneum on Dynamic Variables Delta PP and PVI During Trendelenburg Position.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of the Pneumoperitoneum on Dynamic Variables Delta PP and PVI During Trendelenburg Position.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
